351
00:37:31,353 --> 00:37:32,953
So whenever I see ducks,

352
00:37:33,152 --> 00:37:34,192
I think of her.

353
00:37:36,112 --> 00:37:37,592
The Hermit Duck's image

354
00:37:38,592 --> 00:37:40,072
is restrained and disciplined.

355
00:37:41,232 --> 00:37:42,632
It reminds me of myself.

356
00:37:45,353 --> 00:37:46,672
So when I saw this pendant,

357
00:37:46,913 --> 00:37:47,993
I immediately wanted it.

358
00:37:48,793 --> 00:37:49,632
I remember

359
00:37:50,672 --> 00:37:52,873
seeing it in some client's car.

360
00:37:53,152 --> 00:37:54,393
And I snatched it right off.

361
00:38:09,393 --> 00:38:11,232
Still no news about your sister?

362
00:38:18,353 --> 00:38:19,473
I'll find her.

363
00:38:21,152 --> 00:38:21,953
